# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-

All wanted data - in XML:

== XML structure
. global
 .. default 1C-disk
. user
 .. login (linux) | uid - ID
 .. default 1C-username - string
 .. default 1C-password - string
. base
 .. ID - ID
 .. relation path (relative to global.default_1C-disk
 .. Title
. userbase
 .. baseID - IDREF
 .. userID - IDREF
 .. 

== Parts:
* XML
 - Load
 - [Save]
* GUI
 - User
 - [Admin]
* run
